{
  "stem": "4284.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father still had not returned from his forced labor camp, and my mother and I were simply wiling away the time waiting for, I guess, history to happen.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, it didn't take very long that we had World War II in September of 1939, at which time, things became even more panicky.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Jews were now gradually rounded up to places unknown.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Crystal Night, or the Kristallnacht, did produce the first arrest of over 30,000 men, who did disappear, [INTERPOSING VOICES] only to return later on to find out that they had gone, in Germany, to build certain camps, certain facilities.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we did have those people that returned tell us that certain things were being built but that had not yet been utilized to the extreme measure that occurred later on.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, obviously, looking back, you understand many more things than you did at the time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You were obviously intimidated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You lived in fear of the unknown.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You were definitely exposed to the cruelty of the-- the population, especially children of your own age.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody felt that they were patriotic to hate, to beat, to report Jews for not even the slightest infraction, which you were careful not to do.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You were arrested for anything whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If you were suspected to have a kind of clandestine radio, or if they did find in your mailbox when you hardly received mail, a newspaper, it was cause for an arrest.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course, my father was in a forced labor camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he would-- they always, of course, chose the male of the household.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, since I was the male of the household, so to speak, you assumed certain responsibilities with your little understanding that you had for a 10-year-old.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
